{"tid":461734,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"急屎個陣，個腦諗咩先可以分散注意力","createTime":"2017-11-08T02:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T04:33:06.000Z","uid":137272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0225cb15dbd6f2064f699bb4b2170cea8248a3f","tid":461734,"uid":137272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:26:10.000Z","msg":"如題，事源小弟每朝都急屎，仲準時過月經<br />\n問題黎啦，急親都係車上邊急，最抵死係次次都係差兩三個站就到目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n，咁無理由喺急個陣即刻出閘搵廁所架<br />\n於是小弟每朝就同自己舊肛門括約肌角力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍過屎嘅巴打都知，越在意舊屎就越辛苦，小弟試過背圓周率，又試過計舊屎出世嗰陣嘅力學，思考埋宇宙起源同人生意義都分散唔到注意力<br />\n<br />\n細佬我而家吊住出左半個頭嘅屎喺肛門，唸住大悲咒求佢唔好出黎住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問咁多位巴打，到底我要點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f70c1e0d66a3c2d72139e1b0e47d1842c8262b4","tid":461734,"uid":4550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:27:13.000Z","msg":"屎眼俾人玩鬆哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3f15c0932552d083d4dd29d97d56eee48814d6","tid":461734,"uid":44333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTTF8_qUYAAqvRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCTTF8_qUYAAqvRC.jpg&h=8c2bea8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1248b0a4488c7510c7ccaae22338e24a37a3c690","tid":461734,"uid":153245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:57:45.000Z","msg":"我中學教過我忍屎法 唔係個個work<br />\n<br />\n輕鬆企定 雙手捉住反手向上拉<br />\n<br />\n拉嘅同時忍屎 拉到你Feel到舊屎上返去"},{"pid":"fd7d620f582841b5f4292132dc458efe77cc2157","tid":461734,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T0